'apk ON KINDLE FIRE' - USE Open ES File Explorer, open the Download folder, and tap to install the Google apps you want. For best results, I recommend installing one app at a time and rebooting after each one. Just click ON the following apps to download the APK file and sideload it ON the Kindle Fire.Feb 10, 2014
