Detailed Billing
$1.99 per month per number.

Minimum Contract Term
Each line requires a month–to–month or two–year contract.

Activation/Upgrade Fees
Activation Fee: $30/line ($40 for two–year contracts).
Upgrade Fee: $30/line ($40 for two–year contracts).

Early Termination Fees
The early termination fee is up to $175, or up to $350 if your contract term results from your purchase of an advanced device (e.g., a smartphone).

Taxes, Surcharges and Fees
The market you are in determines taxes, surcharges and fees, such as E911 and gross receipt charges. As of April 1, 2017, they can add between 7% and 46% to your standard monthly access and other charges. Monthly Federal Universal Service (17.4% of the interstate and international telecom charges, as of April 1, 2017; varies quarterly based ON FCC rate), Regulatory (21¢ per voice line, 2¢ per data only line) and Administrative ($1.23 per voice line, 6¢ per data only line) charges are Verizon Wireless charges, not taxes, and are subject to change. For more details ON these charges, call 1–888–684–1888.

